INSERT INTO `video` (`vdid`, `vdtitle`, `category`, `vdUrl`, `overview`, `addedDate`, `target`) VALUES
(1, 'How To Diamond PushUp', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How To Diamond PushUp.mp4', 'Diamond push-ups, also known as triangle push-ups, are a more advanced variation of the classic push-up. Practice diamond push-ups by bringing your hands to close together to form a diamond or triangle shape below your chest. Keep your back and legs in a straight line and push yourself off the ground.', '2021-06-12 12:22:45', 'Chest'),
(2, 'How to Do a Barbell Bench Press ', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/How to Do a Barbell Bench Press.mp4', 'Lie flat on your back on a bench.\r\nGrip the bar with hands just wider than shoulder-width apart, so when you are at the bottom of your move your hands are directly above your elbows. This allows for maximum force generation.\r\nBring the bar slowly down to your chest as you breathe in.\r\nPush up as you breathe out, gripping the bar hard and watching a spot on the ceiling rather than the bar, so you can ensure it travels the same path every time.', '2021-06-12 12:31:35', 'Chest'),
(3, 'How To Bench Dip', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How To Bench Dip.mp4', 'Come down trying for about 90-degree angle with your elbows. And then push straight up like that keep your core tight 12 the whole exercise. And then breathe out on the way up flex those triceps', '2021-06-19 17:42:32', 'Arms'),
(4, ' The Perfect Push Up  Do it right', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - The Perfect Push Up  Do it right.mp4', 'Press through the floor. Come. All the way down squeeze. The back again abs tight. Press through the floor. Come. All the way down squeeze.', '2021-06-19 17:43:28', 'Chest'),
(5, 'How to Do a Dumbbell Biceps Curl  Arm Workout', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do a Dumbbell Biceps Curl  Arm Workout.mp4', 'Stand holding a dumbbell in each hand with your arms hanging by your sides. Ensure your elbows are close to your torso and your palms facing forward. Keeping your upper arms stationary, exhale as you curl the weights up to shoulder level while contracting your biceps. Use a thumb-less grip.', '2021-06-19 17:44:24', 'Arms'),
(6, ' How to Do a Hammer Curl  Arm Workout', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do a Hammer Curl  Arm Workout.mp4', 'You''re going to have the weights perpendicular to the floor all right just like the holding hammer. So start right here 90 degrees. Bring the arms down.\r\n', '2021-06-19 17:45:16', 'Arms'),
(7, 'How to do Crunches', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - HOW TO DO CRUNCHES  Perfect Crunch FOR BEGINNERS  Best ABS Exercises  FITNESS SPECIAL  WORKOUT.mp4', 'If you''re looking for a way to strengthen your abdominal muscles, try crunches. Crunches are exercises you need to do if you want great abs and core. It works the rectums abdominal muscle. Since crunches exercise is more controlled, it can help you improve your focus on your exercise routine. And as it does not use any equipment, you can do it anywhere. This exercise can also improve your muscle strength and flexibility. Try it out!', '2021-06-19 17:46:49', 'Abdominal'),
(8, 'How to Do a Sit Ups Properly', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do a SitUp Properly  Gym Workout.mp4', 'a sit-up means that we''re coming from the floor into sitting up.  All right.  Now your feet must stay on the floor.  The thing that people do mostly wrong in the gym is they tug on their neck and try to get themselves up.  And do this:  one, and back, and back.  And that''s wrong.  All right.  ', '2021-06-23 12:10:18', 'Abdominal'),
(9, 'How To Plank', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How To Plank.mp4', 'The plank is a great core exercise that doesn''t involve doing any crunches. In fact, the basic plank doesn''t involve moving at all. This is referred to as an isometric exercise.  \r\n\r\nThe key with the plank is to engage you core muscles in the right way so that through the effort of balancing and stabilizing your body, you are giving your core muscles a fantastic workout.  And if you don''t think you can get a good workout by holding still, just wait until you try to hold a plank for 30-60 seconds... you''re going to feel it!', '2021-06-23 12:11:34', 'Abdominal'),
(10, 'How to do a Squat for beginner', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - Squats For Beginners How to do a Squat Correctly.mp4', 'We squat all the time - doing yard work, picking things up off the ground, and just the movement that comes along with sitting, to name a few examples.  So building strength in your legs by adding the squat to your exercise routine is a smart way to help prevent injuries while doing your everyday activities.\r\n\r\nDoing squats with bad form can turn the exercise against you though, so it is important to begin doing squats by learning how to do a squat with the correct form.  This video will show you the key components.', '2021-06-23 12:16:02', 'Legs'),
(11, '  Bench Press  for women', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/Women  Bench Press.mp4', 'Upper body workouts can be particularly challenging for beginners to heavy lifting. If you’re just getting started, make sure you start light and focus on form. this video shows how to do a bench press.', '2021-06-23 12:21:43', 'Chest'),
(12, 'PushUp for women', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/PushUp for women.mp4', 'Pushups are a great exercise to build strength and one of the most popular body workouts around.  follow these steps :\r\n\r\nKeep your neck in a neutral position\r\nTuck your elbows to your body\r\nKeep your core nice and tight\r\nSqueeze glutes\r\nKeep toes and hands firmly on the ground\r\nkeep your body in a straight line', '2021-06-23 12:24:20', 'Shoulders'),
(14, 'Calf Exercises for Men ', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/Calf Exercises for Men _ Exercises for Staying Fit.mp4', 'Calf exercises for men include the calf raise, which you can actually do in three different ways depending on your preferences. Find out about calf exercises for men with help from an expert who has been well-known in the fitness industry for over ten years in this free video clip.', '2021-06-27 16:59:18', 'Legs'),
(15, 'How to Do Triceps Bench Dips for women', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do Triceps Bench Dips.mp4', 'Triceps dips on the bench, are exercises that are well known and appreciated for the work done on triceps, pectorals, and front deltoids. \r\nAmong the different variations of "Dips", this is particularly suitable for both workouts at a gym or at home because, if you do not have a fitness bench, you can use any other type of support, such as a simple chair.', '2021-06-27 17:02:25', 'Arms'),
(16, 'How to do the Kneeling Push Up', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to do the perfect KNEELING PUSH UP technique and common mistakes.mp4', 'Difficulty: EasyImpact Level: Normal\r\nTarget Body Parts: abs, triceps, upper back, chest, shoulders\r\n\r\nStart at the top of the push-up position with your hands on the floor, arms straight and underneath your shoulders. Step your knees back behind you so that there is a straight line through your body from your knees up to your head. Engage your glutes, tense your legs and brace your core to keep your body rigid.\r\n\r\nKeeping your elbows in towards your ribs and your forearms vertical, bend at the elbows to lower your body towards the floor. Your head and shoulders should move forwards of your ha', '2021-06-27 17:07:43', 'Shoulders'),
(17, 'How to Do a Hammer Curl for women', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do a Hammer Curl  Female Bodybuilding.mp4', 'Hammer curl, called that because it looks kind of like a hammer. So instead of having your palms facing up, like you do with most bicep exercises, you''re going to have the weight perpendicular to the floor. All right? Just like you''re holding a hammer. \r\n\r\nSo start right here, 90 degrees. Bring the arms down and all the way back up. Arms down, and all the way back up. Now an important thing here is to make sure that the elbow is not swinging. If the elbow moves, or if your back moves, you''re not really using the bicep very much. So make sure that that elbow stays stable as you bring it up and ', '2021-06-27 17:10:10', 'Arms'),
(18, 'How to Do Crunches for women', 'Exercise and Fitness', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to Do Crunches.mp4', 'To do a crunch:\r\n\r\n1. Lie down on your back. Plant your feet on the floor, hip-width apart. Bend your knees and place your arms across your chest. Contract your abs and inhale.\r\n2. Exhale and lift your upper body, keeping your head and neck relaxed.\r\n3. Inhale and return to the starting position.', '2021-06-27 17:13:21', 'Abdominal'),
(19, '10 Healthy Food Swaps You Never Thought To Try', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/yt1s.com - 10 Healthy Food Swaps You Never Thought To Try.mp4', 'Slow and steady wins the race when it comes to getting back into shape. While complete diet makeovers can be overwhelming, focusing on small and easy changes makes healthy eating more manageable and sustainable for a long period.\r\n\r\nThe great thing about these changes is you don’t have to stop it, just swap it.', '2021-07-06 12:21:39', ''),
(20, 'How to EASILY Kick Start A Healthy Lifestyle FAST', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/yt1s.com - How to EASILY Kick Start A Healthy Lifestyle FAST For FREE.mp4', 'A healthy lifestyle simply means doing things that make you happy and feel good. For one person, that may mean walking a mile five times a week, eating healthy food, and spending virtual or in-person time with loved ones every other day.', '2021-07-06 12:22:13', ''),
(21, 'How to be happy', 'Well-being & Happiness', 'uploads/Want to know how to be happy_ Watch this.mp4', 'To find long-term happiness, you need to retrain your brain from a negative mindset to a positive mindset, Celebrate little victories, Practice mindfulness, Accept imperfection, Do what you love, Spend wisely, Live in the moment, Listen to and engage with music, Build meaningful relationships, Cultivate gratitude, Spend time in nature.\r\n\r\nIn this video, Gaur Gopal das ji tells us how to be happy.', '2021-07-10 08:50:42', ''),
(22, '7 Ways to Be Happier, According to Yale Professor of Well-Being', 'Well-being & Happiness', 'uploads/7 Ways to Be Happier, According to Yale Professor of Well-Being.mp4', 'Everything you think you know about ‘happiness’ is dead wrong — here are 7 scientific ways you can rewire your life to be happier.\r\nIn US news and current events today, Yale professor of psychology Laurie Santos sat down with NowThis News to explain how we can all be happier. According to Yale University prof Laurie Santos, happiness can be achieved through practice using science and personal development.', '2021-07-10 08:52:52', ''),
(23, 'The Secret To Real Happiness', 'Well-being & Happiness', 'uploads/The Secret To Real Happiness.mp4', 'Be you and be cool with it. It is the secret to happiness, fulfillment, and making a truly unique impact on the world. As Oscar Wilde said, "Be yourself. Everyone else is already taken. "The Secret To Real Happiness is within youself.', '2021-07-10 08:54:21', ''),
(24, 'Indian Healthy Eating Plate To Stay Healthy', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/Indian Healthy Eating Plate To Stay Healthy.mp4', 'A healthy plate includes each of the food groups: fruits, vegetables, protein, grains, and dairy. Every meal may not achieve this but averaging about one serving of each food group and most meals will get you that much closer to meeting your health goals. Follow these tips to stay healthy: Fat-free and low-fat dairy products, such as low-fat yoghurt, cheese, and milk. Protein foods, such as lean meat, fish, poultry without skin, beans, and peas. Whole-grain foods, such as whole-wheat bread, oatmeal, and brown rice.', '2021-07-10 09:03:36', ''),
(25, 'Keto Recipe - Low Carb Pancake Sandwich', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/Keto Recipe - Low Carb Pancake Sandwich To Lose Weight.mp4', 'This keto breakfast sandwich is low in carbs, high in healthy fats and off the charts in flavor! The yummy sausage will make you forget the missing bread! These Keto breakfast sandwiches are delicious and pack all of the right macros.\r\n\r\nTry this delicious recipe while you are on keto diet.', '2021-07-10 17:49:22', ''),
(26, 'How to Create a Healthy Plate', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/How to Create a Healthy Plate.mp4', 'You should create a healthy foundation for every meal by filling half your plate with fruits and vegetables. Divide the remaining half between a serving of grains — preferably whole grains — and a serving of lean protein. A serving of low-fat or fat-free dairy rounds out each meal.\r\n\r\nFollow this awesome trick to create a Healthy Plate.', '2021-07-10 17:54:18', ''),
(27, 'How to Develop Healthy Eating Habits', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/How to Develop Healthy Eating Habits.mp4', 'You can always develop Healthy Eating Habits while being persistent.', '2021-07-10 17:55:36', ''),
(28, 'Healthy Meal Swaps For The Day', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/Healthy Meal Swaps For The Day.mp4', 'To lose weight you need to start a healthy diet plan and swap your daily snacks with some healthy meal swaps.', '2021-07-10 17:57:18', ''),
(29, 'OATMEAL Recipe for weight loss', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/THE BEST OATMEAL RECIPE FOR WEIGHT LOSS _ HEALTHY BREAKFAST IDEAS FOR WEIGHT LOSS WITH OATS.mp4', 'OATMEAL RECIPE FOR WEIGHT LOSS', '2021-07-10 17:59:29', ''),
(30, 'How trans fats effect your body ', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/Zero trans fat_ Eat less fat live a healthier life!.mp4', 'Trans fats are really bad for health. let''s swap it with healthier food products.', '2021-07-10 18:03:53', ''),
(31, 'The Science of Healthy Eating', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/The Science of Healthy Eating.mp4', 'The Healthy Eating Plate is based on the latest and best scientific evidence, which shows that a plant-based diet rich in vegetables, whole grains, healthy fats, and healthy proteins lowers the risk of weight gain and chronic disease.\r\nChoose health over taste.', '2021-07-10 18:05:55', ''),
(32, 'Salad Recipe To Lose Weight Fast', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/Salad Recipe To Lose Weight Fast.mp4', 'These yummy salads can help you lose weight. ', '2021-07-10 18:08:01', ''),
(33, 'How to Follow a Healthy Vegetarian Diet', 'Healthy Eating', 'uploads/How to Follow a Healthy Vegetarian Diet.mp4', 'A vegetarian diet should include a diverse mix of fruits, vegetables, grains, healthy fats and proteins. To replace the protein provided by meat in your diet, include a variety of protein-rich plant foods like nuts, seeds, legumes, tempeh, tofu and seitan.\r\n\r\nTips to follow a Healthy Vegetarian Diet.', '2021-07-10 18:10:21', ''),
(34, 'Boiled Egg Recipes For Weight Loss', 'Weight Loss', 'uploads/4 Boiled Egg Recipes For Weight Loss.mp4', 'Eggs are a low-calorie food rich in protein and other nutrients. Eating eggs may support weight loss, especially if a person incorporates them into a calorie-controlled diet. Research suggests that eggs boost metabolic activity and increase feelings of fullness. You must try this amazing egg recipes for weight loss.', '2021-07-10 18:13:07', '');

